The paper discusses machine learning automation tools and proposes using types for checking correctness and searching over hyperparameters and pipeline configurations. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses an embedded language that extends the reach of existing automation tools across data modalities and programming languages, indicating that it may also belong to the Software Engineering (cs.SE), Programming Languages (cs.PL), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
